Needs better name:
django-descriptions
django-snippet
django-snppt
django-note
django-text
django-content
django-cms


- Descriptions are snippets of content with a head and a body
- the snippet content can be 'plain', 'html' or 'markdown'

- A page with pieces of content should be buildable by ajax calls
- A page with pieces of content should be buildable without ajax calls
- A page using descriptions in browser should be able to show edit buttons on
  pieces of content which show an edit form on click
